                       OverloadedStrings
  default-extensions:  ExistentialQuantification
                       FlexibleContexts
                       FlexibleInstances
                       GADTs
                       GeneralizedNewtypeDeriving
                       ImportQualifiedPost
                       LambdaCase
                       MultiParamTypeClasses
                       RankNTypes
                       ScopedTypeVariables
                       TupleSections
                       TypeApplications
                       TypeFamilies
                       TypeOperators
